{"tid":1358534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！何妖回辦事處途中被打","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T03:07:36.000Z","uid":5526,"like":6,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"463f7b8ca56f20a943f2f4975ae9fda6e18951e2","tid":1358534,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:58:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講撚夠依條撚樣未啊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線義士呢？黑警沒交代啊！今日仲話無喺橋開槍啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推撚爆佢</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">！重回正軌！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">追究黑警濫權</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有五大訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上環Video 整合 (粗略) (keep updating) <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=99469bda\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n<br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=ac687342\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n<br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=7e984dd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n<br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=32067f64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n<br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=7ab049a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n<br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=19a84b58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n<br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=592fbeaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n<br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=3f5c4db1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n<br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=66e89220\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n<br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=7895a5a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n<br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=a28b638c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n\t <br />\n<br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=e264b6a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=9cd1c179\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t <br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=08189750\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n\t <br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=b97043b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n\t <br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplePhotographers%2Fphotos%2Fa.1131233677080155%2F1131269430409913%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=d8551e20\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n7.21民陣大遊行 | 警方平射角度開槍清場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEsy4jTTOpYI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=2dca49bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n\t <br />\n有記者直接被催淚彈打中（07.21）譴責警察暴力：記者被催淚彈打中，係直接打中！[/quote]"},{"pid":"e18e1f10376a399c719a0f2be44db0db28d16b25","tid":1358534,"uid":165246,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"da256cdec998e94b25c89964d66bb38ee8317413","tid":1358534,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"097f8574b61c0e96bb18838dfbd51a6394f66cb4","tid":1358534,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04a8b8e948f8791198f4ffc0f207fc1f41d1367c","tid":1358534,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"係就好"},{"pid":"451795f5854c15dd49cd4e690945593faec7f58a","tid":1358534,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:00:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eee291a45b31f38fe754c2e2d4b013f4ea42a99","tid":1358534,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:00:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ee053fb31ca00e56ccf9e24dfee9ccdf8cec32a","tid":1358534,"uid":157222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35f0e7ed545702f338c2358b52c91576388e45b6","tid":1358534,"uid":190277,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:01:02.000Z","msg":"玩夠假標題未？"},{"pid":"3ca656f65603c24c22491bda4ea65b7d982fc884","tid":1358534,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:01:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c99e37edf38a4dbe61d46905c3c7c5e85faba44f","tid":1358534,"uid":5526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,